						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
							An artistic Request for Proposal exploring protocols for communication between different forms of intelligence. A framework for intelligence-form-agnostic communication and collaboration.
						</p>
						<div class="inline-flex items-center text-tomato-600 font-medium">
							View on GitHub
